\int \frac{4x^2 -20}{(2x+5)^3}dx = \int \dfrac A{(2x + 5)} + \dfrac B{(2x + 5)^2} + \dfrac C{(2x + 5)^3}\, dx
A(2x + 5)^2 + B(2x + 5) + C = 4x^2 - 20\tag{1}
x = -\frac 52
